```mermaid
---
title: WBS Task State Machine / WBS 任務狀態機
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> Pending : Task created and assigned\n任務建立並完成指派

    Pending --> InProgress : Assignee starts task\n指派人開始任務

    InProgress --> Done : Assignee submits snapshot\nand CR is approved\n提交快照且 CR 核准

    InProgress --> Blocked : Issue opened (#1 #2 #3)\n開立議題

    Blocked --> InProgress : Issue resolved\n議題解決

    Done --> QAInReview : Submitted for QA\n提交質檢

    QAInReview --> AcceptanceReview : QA passed\nQA 通過

    QAInReview --> InProgress : QA failed\nAttach issue reference\nQA 未通過，附議題引用

    AcceptanceReview --> Accepted : Acceptance approved\n驗收通過

    AcceptanceReview --> InProgress : Acceptance rejected\nAttach feedback\n驗收拒絕，附回饋

    Accepted --> [*] : Triggers Settlement Layer\n觸發結算層

    state InProgress {
        direction LR
        Editing --> Reviewing : Submit snapshot\n提交快照
        Reviewing --> Editing : Changes requested\n要求修改
        Reviewing --> ReadyToSubmit : CR approved\nCR 核准
    }

    state AcceptanceReview {
        direction LR
        StakeholderCheck --> SignOff : Requirements met\n符合需求
        StakeholderCheck --> Rework : Requirements not met\n不符合需求
    }

    note right of Pending
        Workforce Scheduling
        has confirmed assignee
        and time window
        人力排程已確認
        指派人與時間窗口
    end note

    note right of Blocked
        Task cannot progress
        until ALL linked issues
        are resolved
        所有關聯議題解決前
        任務無法繼續
    end note

    note right of Accepted
        AR record created
        AP record created
        應收 / 應付帳款建立
    end note
```
